
Life cycle of a Variable

1. Declaration of a variable
2. Initialization of a variable
3. Utilization of a variable

Types of Variables

1. Based on the location of a variable
	a. Local Variable (temporary variable)
	b. Global Variable
		i. static variable
		ii. non-static variable / instance variable / data-members 
	
2. Based on the value of a variable
	a. Premitive type variable
	b. Reference type variable
	
	